@thinkerou Thanks for the contributions. Sorry for not responding to this for so long. The PHP extension has gone thru quite a lot of changes in the last few releases and I want to stabilize things as much as possible before accepting changes. Now we are in a better state to accept this. Do you mind cleaning this up - rebase to the latest `master`, squash it up and I will take a look again?

Thanks.
